# ðŸ”¢ Token Counter for Greek Texts (Meltemi-7B)

This script counts the number of tokens across a folder of `.txt` files using the `Meltemi-7B-v1.5` tokenizer from Hugging Face.

## ðŸ“¦ What It Does

- Recursively walks through a folder of `.txt` files
- Handles both `UTF-8` and `ISO-8859-7` encodings
- Counts characters and tokens per file
- Prints total token count across all files

